227
00:17:02,797 --> 00:17:05,237
<i>Nechceš vedieť, ako sme vtedy žili,</i>

228
00:17:09,197 --> 00:17:11,567
<i>aké boli naše posledné okamihy,</i>

229
00:17:13,567 --> 00:17:15,267
